marketing: Shell Spirax S6 ATF VM Plus Oil is a premium performance, automatic transmission fluid specifically designed for use in Voith Turbo transmissions. Spirax S6 ATF VM Plus is recommended for extended oil drain intervals in the DIWA.6 and DIWA.5 transmissions for 180,000km, while it is also suitable for DIWA.3E and older DIWA transmissions at the extended oil drain interval of 120,000km.
